Created attachment 695
Patch to allow loading file from contribution's resource folder

With the attached patch to the loader template , it is possible to load a file from the contribution's source folder if the following jobs are added to the "jobs" key:

 "jobs" :
  {
    "source-script" :
    {
      "add-script" :
      [ 
        {
          "uri" : "persist:resource/persist/persist-all-min.js"
        }
      ]
    },
    "build-script" :
    {
      "add-script" :
      [ 
        {
          "uri" : "persist:resource/persist/persist-all-min.js"
        }
      ]
    }    
  }

What the patch does is to resolve the path through the prefix, just like the normal qooxdoo class files. Tested against the demo app in the "Persist" contribution. It works with FF source and build, but doesn't with Chrome in "build" mode.
